From: Oleksandr Natalenko <oleksandr@natalenko.name>
Subject: [pf-curated-6.14] amd-pstate: AMD-pstate enhancements

Re-cut from natalenko's pf-kernel branch amd-pstate-6.14 (tip 8778c1565da9)
as a single bulk diff, restricted to the files this overlay's curation
kept on the 6.14 slot. Source: codeberg.org/pf-kernel/linux.

---
